  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "02837a063f8b865c5550378320f174c3910049bd709cb9ed9b75799b6b8f02c4": "Hmm... Nahta will know what to do with these. [?], take them to him in Cam Torum's magic shop. Tell him I sent you.",
    "1a4130f0c1a944c7c1487f188a7ece4456e06c2f72e83549c5052325059b0f83": "This is an old place, [?]. Older even than much of what we dwarves remember.",
    "20d1b2728c73acbc12c13ea3bf486835a218d4fe25d0783896b4be89e9d0523a": "[?], he's your responsibility now. If either of you cause any trouble, you're both out!",
    "2a4949e71fe06d28a849dee4a398dbec4b04ca375747bd570bcee371948cb28f": "Hmph. It's fine. Your intentions are good, [?], which is more than can be said for most of your kind. Who knows, maybe one or two dwarves here might even grow to tolerate you.",
    "4b9fb38a75497f16bbb6c7f12c6f30ed62200a92cd785743e86b306208d919a9": "I'll gather some guards and see if we can find Teumo. While I do that, [?], you should go to Neypotzli and find the cultists.",
    "5bddfc2e2ff3cc638d520f8ad7fad5da3f1caf983133bc8fdd1b6e1016365931": "Hello there, [?]. What can I do for you?",
    "7510032320670f5aa9ed5700e2f5683dc7d990a4b0f9c20cc821a57b8f20a887": "You'll need to make some space for those two talismans [?].",
    "794bdf580ae765a10948c29bc50c808f42c08855e4f915b72ac2ad8d17c6e64b": "Hello there, [?]. I hear that cultist business of yours ended up getting sorted. Your Queen traded Teumo with the Highlord in return for a new mineral deal.",
    "7a254d26bde24352de48e1b93c003a473dd9d655cd9c31395c3501249e1ca585": "You know as well as I do, [?], these cultists are fools. There is no world ending threat here, nor any threat to Cam Torum. This is a human problem. It's for humans to deal with.",
    "8524ea67fa03ebb8f7953500cf4898e0f18aaa656c5f971cadfc0e0312d2d56a": "You can join [?].",
    "8cc787df2e2c31741772f1f76d0a66bb3d41bd822fa21ce26a975d4427bcd9be": "When I vouched for you back there, [?], I wasn't expecting you to bring a Teokan with you.",
    "b09391419dc7dc4e86c72ff58abbb0c557a738dd8a10053849434c50b3b0cb4b": "I will wait for you in the market, [?]. I have some ideas for where you might begin your search.",
    "dd0462326796236694509706d75931d51aa6377802760cc67109c012b763f12a": "There you are, [?]. That nagua told us how to find you.",
    "ecaf563b50be2a3bdf4b08dca2e7ac783bdc544fca0e3fe594641602568a6c5e": "You have my gratitude, [?]. You have helped to ensure Cam Torum's safety. You will always be welcome back."
  }
}